Jaleswar is a small town in Odisha state, India. It comes under Baleshwar district.

Jaleswar is well connected through railway lines and by road with Kolkata and Bhubaneswar. 
Nearest Airports - Kolkata (around 200 km) and Bhubaneswar (around 275 km).
